      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a truly exceptional vehicle in mint condition! This car is as close to showroom-perfect as you'll find on the used market \u2014 the exterior gleams without a blemish, and the interior is immaculate, fresh, and beautifully preserved. Every system runs flawlessly, and the attention to care this vehicle has received really shows. If you want the very best, this is it!",
