      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Affordable and ready to roll! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and handles everyday driving well, but does show its age with some visible wear and minor imperfections inside and out. It's not perfect, but it's a practical, budget-friendly option for someone who needs reliable transportation without the premium price tag. Come take a look and see if it's the right fit for you!",
