    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that won't break the bank? This car is in good condition \u2014 it drives smoothly, has been well-maintained, and is ready to hit the road with confidence! You'll notice some minor cosmetic wear consistent with normal use, but nothing that takes away from its solid, dependable character. The mechanical components are in great shape, making this a smart buy for anyone who wants quality without paying top dollar. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll be impressed!",
      "price": 34000.0,
