    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "We're listing this vehicle honestly as a car in poor condition, and we want any potential buyer to have a fully realistic picture before reaching out. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 expect noticeable rust, dents, and paint that is faded and peeling in multiple areas. The interior is similarly worn, with torn upholstery, cracked dashboard panels, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, this vehicle has known issues and will likely require substantial repairs before it can be considered reliably road-worthy. This listing is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project car, or seeking parts. We are not hiding anything \u2014 what you see is what you get, and we encourage an in-person inspection before purchase.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture of what that means. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a healthy shine with only minor surface scratches and light swirl marks consistent with normal use. There are no significant dents or rust concerns, though a close inspection will reveal the small imperfections you'd expect from a pre-owned vehicle with real-world history. The interior is clean and comfortable, with upholstery showing moderate wear on the driver's seat and some light scuffing on interior trim pieces \u2014 nothing that detracts from daily enjoyment, but worth noting for buyers expecting showroom freshness. Mechanically, this car has been well maintained: it starts reliably, drives smoothly, and all major systems \u2014 brakes, steering, HVAC, and electronics \u2014 are functioning as they should. Tires have solid tread remaining. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that has been cared for and is ready for its next owner without requiring immediate repairs or significant investment. A great choice for buyers who want honest, reliable transportation at a fair price.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in fair condition, and the asking price reflects that honestly \u2014 please read this full description before reaching out. The car is drivable and functional for everyday use, but it does show its age and history. Expect some cosmetic wear including scratches, scuffs, and minor dents on the exterior, along with interior wear consistent with regular use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some maintenance attention in the near term \u2014 nothing catastrophic, but not a worry-free situation either. There are no major undisclosed surprises; what you see is what you get. This is a solid option for a buyer who wants reliable basic transportation and is comfortable with a vehicle that isn't in showroom shape. Ideal for someone handy or willing to invest a modest amount in upkeep. Priced to reflect the condition fairly.",
      "price": 16000.0,
